1
00:00:14,090 --> 00:00:20,390
♪Suddenly, you showed up♪

2
00:00:22,150 --> 00:00:28,750
♪Who stole away those years♪

3
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:37,320
♪Oh, night and day♪

4
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:45,540
♪Oh, it's been a long time♪

5
00:00:45,930 --> 00:00:50,050
♪Pass through the bustling world
in the daytime♪

6
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:53,880
♪Circumvent love at night♪

7
00:00:54,010 --> 00:00:57,760
♪Day after day, year after year♪

8
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:02,040
♪I wake up and close my eyes
before it gets dark♪

9
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:06,140
♪But when the day breaks into the night♪

10
00:01:06,140 --> 00:01:10,220
♪It makes me believe
that there's still love♪

11
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:14,050
♪If you want it, if I want it♪

12
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:20,800
♪It's a vow of night and day♪

13
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:32,890
♪It's a vow of day and night♪

14
00:01:32,890 --> 00:01:37,200
[Blooming]

15
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:39,920
[Episode 16]

16
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,190
Qiu Yuebai?

17
00:01:42,870 --> 00:01:43,800
Are you here for noodles too?

18
00:01:44,870 --> 00:01:45,590
I'm just passing by.

19
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,680
A group of Hu merchants
came from the west.

20
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:47,800
I’m going to visit them.

21
00:01:48,590 --> 00:01:49,680
Would you like to come with me?

22
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:51,080
Let's go.

23
00:01:51,270 --> 00:01:53,400
But what about the noodles?

24
00:01:54,230 --> 00:01:55,510
We won't get our turn

25
00:01:55,510 --> 00:01:56,630
for another hour.

26
00:01:56,830 --> 00:01:58,720
Let's go and have a look.

27
00:02:00,630 --> 00:02:03,120
Girls all like jewelry.

28
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:07,400
Let's go.

29
00:02:07,630 --> 00:02:08,360
- Hurry.
- Go.

30
00:02:19,190 --> 00:02:21,630
If you don't bring this soup to Cui Chen,

31
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:22,910
it'll boil away.

32
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:26,440
He already ate what I cooked yesterday.

33
00:02:27,030 --> 00:02:28,110
I still have a lot left.

34
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,320
Would you like to try it?

35
00:02:30,030 --> 00:02:32,160
You're such a diligent
and perfect girlfriend.

36
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,630
You made two pots of porridge a night.

37
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:36,720
Cui Chen just said he's not feeling well

38
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:37,830
and wants to sleep early.

39
00:02:38,670 --> 00:02:39,600
I think

40
00:02:39,830 --> 00:02:42,520
as a cultivator
with such profound attainments,

41
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,240
if he's not feeling well,

42
00:02:43,470 --> 00:02:44,270
it must be because

43
00:02:44,270 --> 00:02:46,240
the wound he got at the Qiqiao Pavilion
hasn't recovered yet.

44
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:49,240
So I adjusted my recipe.

45
00:02:49,830 --> 00:02:51,550
I hope it'll help him to recover.

46
00:02:53,190 --> 00:02:54,630
I can't stand you being lovey-dovey.

47
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:55,830
I'm going to bed.

48
00:02:55,830 --> 00:02:57,190
Have some porridge first.

49
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:58,750
No, thanks.

50
00:02:59,190 --> 00:03:01,600
It stinks of love.

51
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:11,190
How long will it take to get there?

52
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:12,600
Where are you going to meet?

53
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,520
We're almost there.

54
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:15,520
Who's that?

55
00:03:16,390 --> 00:03:17,080
This...

56
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:18,240
Senior Mu Bai?

57
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,670
No way.

58
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:22,750
He is with Tantan at the Yunlai Inn.

59
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:23,800
It can't be him.

60
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:24,960
I'm a pigeon.

61
00:03:25,190 --> 00:03:26,320
With my clairvoyance,

62
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:28,000
how could I mistake him
for someone else?

63
00:03:34,390 --> 00:03:34,910
Tantan.

64
00:03:35,390 --> 00:03:35,880
Tantan.

65
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:36,670
Tantan.

66
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:38,550
Tantan.

67
00:03:39,550 --> 00:03:40,390
Why are you here?

68
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:41,600
What's going on?

69
00:03:42,110 --> 00:03:42,630
Well...

70
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:46,800
Tantan, do you know
where Senior Mu Bai is?

71
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,160
In his room.

72
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,390
He said he wasn't feeling well,

73
00:03:50,390 --> 00:03:51,390
so he went to bed early.

74
00:03:52,110 --> 00:03:52,550
Well...

75
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:53,880
Tantan,

76
00:03:54,390 --> 00:03:55,240
we just saw

77
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:58,000
Senior Mu Bai

78
00:03:58,110 --> 00:03:59,520
flying over to a lotus courtyard.

79
00:04:00,110 --> 00:04:01,190
It must be a mistake.

80
00:04:01,390 --> 00:04:01,960
It's true.

81
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,600
We even asked around.

82
00:04:03,670 --> 00:04:04,750
Guess who I saw?

83
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:07,190
Who?

84
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,000
The owner of the Shihua Pavilion

85
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,910
who looks just like you.

86
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:17,550
Tantan.

87
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,350
- Tantan.
- Tantan.

88
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:19,320
Well...

89
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:20,230
You stay here.

90
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:22,550
You have to look after Uncle Zi Meng.

91
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,510
You stay. I'll go.

92
00:04:23,510 --> 00:04:24,480
No.

93
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,230
Xueyi.

94
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:27,600
You must be careful.

95
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:28,880
I know.

96
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:29,720
Xueyi.

97
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,270
Tell me if anyone bullies you.

98
00:04:31,550 --> 00:04:32,550
I'll beat them up.

99
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,040
Watch me...

100
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:47,760
Chill out.

101
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:55,480
Tantan, Mr. Cui must have his reason

102
00:04:55,670 --> 00:04:56,760
to come here late at night.

103
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:01,720
I believe in Cui Chen's moral quality

104
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,790
and his loyalty to me.

105
00:05:03,350 --> 00:05:04,510
I'm sure he won't fool around.

106
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:06,480
Whatever it is,

107
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,550
he shouldn't have come out

108
00:05:07,550 --> 00:05:09,390
to meet another girl at midnight
without telling you.

109
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:13,350
There must be something
he can't tell me.

110
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:14,950
I think the courtyard
is quite secretive.

111
00:05:15,270 --> 00:05:16,830
Possibly,
Lian Rong invited Mr. Cui over.

112
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,110
What does Lian Rong have

113
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:20,950
to tell Senior Mu Bai privately?

114
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,040
A man and a woman meet secretly
in the middle of the night.

115
00:05:23,550 --> 00:05:24,350
I'm going to see

116
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,880
what they are talking about.

117
00:05:34,790 --> 00:05:36,350
I asked you to come here alone.

118
00:05:36,670 --> 00:05:38,160
I hope you don't mind.

119
00:05:39,230 --> 00:05:40,880
Please cut to the chase.

120
00:05:42,110 --> 00:05:45,000
Sir, don't you think I look familiar?

121
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,350
What do you mean?

122
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:54,000
I often dream of Mr. Cui.

123
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:57,640
In my dreams, we're very close.

124
00:05:58,270 --> 00:06:01,040
But the girl with you

125
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,390
looks just like me.

126
00:06:02,790 --> 00:06:04,270
So I dare not tell you everything

127
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:06,160
for fear of jeopardizing
your relationship.

128
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,110
You say we are very close.

129
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,550
How close we are exactly?

130
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:14,110
I want to know

131
00:06:14,510 --> 00:06:17,480
what's your relationship with that girl.

132
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,600
She is my junior.

133
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:25,720
What a coincidence.

134
00:06:26,830 --> 00:06:28,720
In my dreams,

135
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,480
we are also a senior and a junior.

136
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:33,720
I often dream about practicing with you

137
00:06:34,110 --> 00:06:36,230
in a mountain where there is a pond.

138
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:40,640
We've discovered a secret place
in the back of the mountain.

139
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:47,880
Sir, you've planted
a pond of lotuses for me.

140
00:06:53,510 --> 00:06:54,320
Have you forgotten?

141
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:58,440
You said I couldn't run away

142
00:06:58,790 --> 00:06:59,790
if I wore it.

143
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,350
Red string.

144
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,320
Lotus pond.

145
00:07:11,950 --> 00:07:13,950
I think I've seen them before.

146
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:16,320
Once you put the destiny string on,

147
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:17,950
you can't run away.

148
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,390
(Why is this red string)

149
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:22,510
(exactly the same
as the one in my dream?)

150
00:07:23,550 --> 00:07:25,040
(Wasn't that my dream?)

151
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:28,110
(But why did I dream)

152
00:07:28,390 --> 00:07:29,760
(about Cui Chen and this woman?)

153
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:35,160
In my dreams,
we often sneak down the mountain,

154
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,920
catch demons,

155
00:07:37,550 --> 00:07:38,720
and pick lotus seedpods together.

156
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,880
But you don't have that thing

157
00:07:48,550 --> 00:07:51,510
on your forehead in my dreams.

158
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:56,200
I remember you told me

159
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,600
that you would always be there for me

160
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,600
and never betray me.

161
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,480
Even if the whole world opposed me,

162
00:08:03,670 --> 00:08:05,200
you would still be there for me.

163
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:09,110
But why are you so cruel to me
in the end?

164
00:08:13,270 --> 00:08:14,880
Enough. Stop it.

165
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:18,670
So these are not my dreams, right?

166
00:08:19,390 --> 00:08:20,720
These are our past.

167
00:08:24,350 --> 00:08:25,040
Tantan,

168
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:26,920
wait for a while.

169
00:08:27,230 --> 00:08:28,320
Let's see what Mr. Cui will do.

170
00:08:29,510 --> 00:08:30,600
You invited me over

171
00:08:31,350 --> 00:08:32,320
and told me about your dreams.

172
00:08:33,110 --> 00:08:34,000
What do you want me to do?

173
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,880
Take me away.

174
00:08:42,550 --> 00:08:44,150
We can start over.

175
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,230
Tantan.

176
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:06,400
Tomorrow we'll return
to the Qingyuan Sect together.

177
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,840
The little spirits in the Lotus Realm

178
00:09:09,470 --> 00:09:10,590
will be happy to see you.

179
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:17,840
OK.

180
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:20,110
I haven't seen them for a long time.

181
00:09:21,790 --> 00:09:23,000
Red lotus flowers
bloom gracefully in the water.

182
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:32,670
Don't you remember?

183
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:36,350
I've lost my memory.

184
00:09:37,350 --> 00:09:38,790
I can't remember many things.

185
00:09:39,670 --> 00:09:42,400
And my memory is fragmented.

186
00:10:00,710 --> 00:10:03,320
Tantan, given Mr. Cui's reaction,

187
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:05,590
was Lian Rong telling the truth?

188
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:07,080
They...

189
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:09,790
They did have a relationship.

190
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:11,840
And they were very close.

191
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,320
More than that.

192
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:15,230
In my opinion, Lian Rong

193
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,960
is the woman Cui Chen used to love.

194
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,110
Didn't you see them

195
00:10:18,110 --> 00:10:19,350
hugging each other?

196
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:21,080
Would you stop?

197
00:10:26,710 --> 00:10:27,760
I can't believe it.

198
00:10:29,350 --> 00:10:31,030
Lian Rong looks exactly like me.

199
00:10:31,880 --> 00:10:33,960
She knows so much
about the Qingyuan Sect.

200
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:35,080
And she...

201
00:10:36,790 --> 00:10:38,200
She also has a thing for Cui Chen.

202
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:40,080
I think Cui Chen

203
00:10:40,110 --> 00:10:41,200
is using you as a substitute.

204
00:10:45,590 --> 00:10:50,110
Tantan, I didn't mean
to call you a substitute.

205
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:51,520
Tantan,

206
00:10:52,150 --> 00:10:54,350
though it's not right for Mr. Cui
to meet someone he loves

207
00:10:54,350 --> 00:10:55,350
behind your back,

208
00:10:55,710 --> 00:10:56,840
I believe

209
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,520
he has real feelings for you.

210
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:01,760
Tantan, no matter what happens,

211
00:11:01,760 --> 00:11:03,110
I'm on your side.

212
00:11:06,910 --> 00:11:07,350
Tantan.

213
00:11:10,030 --> 00:11:10,960
There, there.

214
00:11:11,350 --> 00:11:12,320
Don't be sad.

215
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,880
You've done a good job tonight.

216
00:11:22,230 --> 00:11:23,960
Master said
you could proceed to step two.

217
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:25,280
Put him at ease.

218
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:27,110
Everything is under my control.

219
00:11:27,790 --> 00:11:29,550
Be careful and stick to the plan.

220
00:11:30,230 --> 00:11:32,150
If Cui Chen gets suspicious
and the plan fails,

221
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:33,440
the consequences will be severe.

222
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:34,440
What will happen?

223
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:36,030
Will he kill me?

224
00:11:37,230 --> 00:11:37,880
Don't go too far.

225
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:41,280
Have a guess.

226
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,510
This time, how sincere

227
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:46,190
is your master to Zhao Tantan?

228
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,120
It's none of your business.

229
00:11:48,510 --> 00:11:49,320
Mind your own business.

230
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,150
Remember,
don't hurt Miss Zhao by mistake.

231
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:54,590
Cui Chen has profound attainments.
Be careful.

232
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,480
Did you say that
on behalf of your master

233
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:57,750
or yourself?

234
00:11:58,150 --> 00:11:58,920
Look out for yourself.

235
00:12:33,510 --> 00:12:34,510
Why are you up so early?

236
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:36,240
You stayed up late cooking soup.

237
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:37,510
Why don't you get more sleep?

238
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:42,240
Did you sleep well last night?

239
00:12:43,560 --> 00:12:45,360
I slept well
after eating the soup you cooked.

240
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:47,750
My stomach was warm all night.

241
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:50,920
So,

242
00:12:51,710 --> 00:12:53,480
is it my soup

243
00:12:54,630 --> 00:12:56,590
or Lian Rong's sweet talk
that tastes better?

244
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,590
Do you want me to help you recall

245
00:13:08,950 --> 00:13:10,630
where you were last night?

246
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:17,320
Yes, I went to see Lian Rong last night

247
00:13:17,830 --> 00:13:19,070
and investigate something in passing.

248
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:20,590
What kind of thing?

249
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,240
I haven't found out about it.

250
00:13:23,950 --> 00:13:24,750
But I'll let you know

251
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:26,320
as soon as I find out.

252
00:13:26,630 --> 00:13:27,440
You must trust me.

253
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:28,560
Trust?

254
00:13:29,630 --> 00:13:31,240
How can I trust you?

255
00:13:32,390 --> 00:13:33,560
Was the so-called investigation

256
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,750
the passionate hours
you spent with Lian Rong?

257
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:38,120
Were you in the courtyard last night?

258
00:13:41,040 --> 00:13:44,190
Yes, I saw you clearly

259
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,560
and heard you loud and clear.

260
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:47,800
Who took you there?

261
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:48,630
Qiu Yuebai?

262
00:13:50,390 --> 00:13:52,270
He had nothing to do with it.
Don't change the subject.

263
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:57,070
Do you know Lian Rong for a long time?

264
00:13:58,590 --> 00:13:59,070
No.

265
00:13:59,590 --> 00:14:00,000
So...

266
00:14:00,830 --> 00:14:02,150
Are you saying

267
00:14:02,590 --> 00:14:04,950
what Lian Rong said last night
was a lie?

268
00:14:07,150 --> 00:14:07,680
No either.

269
00:14:09,190 --> 00:14:10,630
Neither this nor that.

270
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:13,000
What are you hiding from me?

271
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,680
I haven't found out what's going on yet.

272
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:16,630
Lian Rong's purpose
and identity are unclear.

273
00:14:16,880 --> 00:14:18,480
It's dangerous for you
to get involved too early.

274
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:19,920
Give me a few more days.

275
00:14:20,070 --> 00:14:20,880
Trust me.

276
00:14:21,390 --> 00:14:22,880
I'll give you
a satisfactory explanation.

277
00:14:28,560 --> 00:14:29,040
Fine.

278
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,800
Let me ask you one last question.

279
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:34,510
Go ahead.

280
00:14:35,710 --> 00:14:39,440
If I ask you to leave Yunlai Town
