312
00:16:43,830 --> 00:16:45,320
since he met you, Tantan.

313
00:16:45,950 --> 00:16:47,750
Who knows if he's bloomed

314
00:16:47,830 --> 00:16:49,750
because of me or my face?

315
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:50,630
Gosh.

316
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,070
Uncle,

317
00:16:52,630 --> 00:16:54,040
what is Tantan talking about?

318
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:55,830
I don't understand a word.

319
00:16:56,590 --> 00:16:57,630
I don't either.

320
00:16:57,630 --> 00:16:58,120
Tantan.

321
00:16:59,630 --> 00:17:01,240
Tantan, something happened.

322
00:17:01,710 --> 00:17:02,920
