all the year round there.

339
00:17:35,390 --> 00:17:37,110
I've always wanted to go there.

340
00:17:38,560 --> 00:17:40,800
No, let's go back to the Qingyuan Sect.

341
00:17:42,040 --> 00:17:43,960
