for over 100 years

369
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:43,560
until

370
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:45,600
I met you.

371
00:18:49,230 --> 00:18:51,960
Not to mention the fact
that you guys unexpectedly found out

372
00:18:51,990 --> 00:18:53,720
about Lian Rong
and Cui Chen's secret meeting.

373
00:18:54,080 --> 00:18:56,390
