417
00:21:25,040 --> 00:21:25,720
I can't sit by

418
00:21:25,720 --> 00:21:28,110
and watch him in danger.

419
00:21:50,150 --> 00:21:50,750
Mr. Cui.

420
00:21:55,750 --> 00:21:56,630
Cui Chen.

421
00:21:58,840 --> 00:21:59,390
Cui Chen.

