Cui Chen!

436
00:22:38,390 --> 00:22:40,630
Kill her!

437
00:22:40,630 --> 00:22:41,750
How could the Qingyuan Sect

438
00:22:41,800 --> 00:22:43,230
take a lotus spirit as its disciple?

439
00:22:43,230 --> 00:22:44,840
The guardian of the Seven-Leaf Lotus

440
00:22:44,840 --> 00:22:46,720
is in league with a lotus spirit!

441
00:22:46,800 --> 00:22:48,350
The Seven-Leaf Lotus is lost

442
00:22:48,390 --> 00:22:50,630
