and plague the world.

444
00:22:54,150 --> 00:22:54,750
Today,

445
00:22:54,840 --> 00:22:57,350
the Qingyuan Sect
must give us an explanation!

446
00:22:57,470 --> 00:22:58,470
Give us an explanation!

447
00:22:58,560 --> 00:23:01,350
The guardian of the Seven-Leaf Lotus
and the lotus spirit?

448
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:02,720
Who are you exactly?

449
00:23:03,840 --> 00:23:04,990
I'm your Lian Wen.

450
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:05,800
Cui Chen.

451
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:06,800
Cui Chen.

452
00:23:07,510 --> 00:23:08,270
Lian Wen?

453
00:23:08,800 --> 00:23:10,040
