459
00:23:26,350 --> 00:23:26,840
Tantan!

460
00:23:26,840 --> 00:23:30,200
Kill her!

461
00:23:43,870 --> 00:23:44,600
Cui Chen!

462
00:23:44,840 --> 00:23:46,840
