463
00:23:47,320 --> 00:23:49,350
I never want to see you again.

464
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:50,920
Cui Chen!

465
00:23:53,320 --> 00:23:53,840
Tantan.

466
00:24:13,600 --> 00:24:14,320
Cui Chen!

467
00:24:28,800 --> 00:24:29,720
Zhao Tantan.

