487
00:27:15,630 --> 00:27:18,390
Qiu, luckily you are not seriously hurt.

488
00:27:18,750 --> 00:27:20,350
Otherwise, I'd be sorry.

489
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:21,630
I won't let you get hurt.

490
00:27:22,680 --> 00:27:23,750
I was hurt because

491
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:24,920
