499
00:27:37,230 --> 00:27:38,150
Do you regard me as an outsider

500
00:27:38,560 --> 00:27:39,470
instead of a friend?

501
00:27:39,560 --> 00:27:40,440
No. How could I...

502
00:27:40,630 --> 00:27:41,270
I'm just kidding.

503
00:27:43,560 --> 00:27:45,270
By the way, I have good news for you.

504
00:27:45,560 --> 00:27:46,990
I've got a tip-off
from the Seven Nights Inn.

505
00:27:47,390 --> 00:27:49,320
