507
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:52,350
There is indeed a lotus seed
in the town.

508
00:27:53,560 --> 00:27:55,390
OK, I'll tell them.

509
00:27:55,750 --> 00:27:56,800
You get some rest.

510
00:28:01,800 --> 00:28:02,320
Huai Meng,

511
00:28:03,230 --> 00:28:04,390
I'll leave Qiu to you.

512
00:28:04,800 --> 00:28:05,990
Don't worry. I'll take care of him.

513
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:24,920
Tantan, are you OK?

514
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:26,470
Why do you still care?

515
00:28:28,510 --> 00:28:28,960
Tantan,

516
00:28:32,440 --> 00:28:33,320
