517
00:28:34,150 --> 00:28:35,870
I approached her to expose her plot.

518
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:40,110
So, you knew there was a problem
with Lian Rong

519
00:28:40,110 --> 00:28:41,110
from the beginning?

520
00:28:42,040 --> 00:28:43,320
Then why did you hide it from me?

521
00:28:44,040 --> 00:28:44,630
Am I

522
00:28:44,630 --> 00:28:46,270
