535
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:25,960
Tantan.

536
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:27,390
Yes.

537
00:29:29,270 --> 00:29:30,680
You and Lian Wen look alike.

538
00:29:30,990 --> 00:29:33,080
But I can tell Tantan from Lian Wen.

539
00:29:34,750 --> 00:29:35,510
100 years ago,

540
00:29:36,630 --> 00:29:38,230
